These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, iris, bellflower, begonia
1. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person eating mango is the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Flower   | iris  | sunflower     | bellflower   | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, amber, yellow, emerald
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the person who likes emerald is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | yellow | emerald | amber | lilac    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, orchid, aconite
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | orchid | aconite | begonia         |

