.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, nigerian, pakistani
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, azure, ebony, aquamarine
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Color           | coral      | ebony | aquamarine | azure    |

