.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, entrepreneur, musician
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, chinese, canadian
1. the canadian is on the right of the designer##1
2. the canadian is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the russian##1
5. the indian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| Nationality   | indian          | russian | chinese     | canadian    |

