.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, nectarine, peach, lemon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, train, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Food    | cauliflower | peach  | nectarine | lemon |
| Transport   | tram | train | taxi          | bus    |

