.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, grapefruit, lettuce, grapes
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the rat is the person eating raspberry##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating lettuce is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | lettuce | grapefruit  | raspberry | grapes   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

