.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, swisher, aristoff, game
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, horror, thriller
1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the swisher-smoker is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar          | bluemaster | aristoff  | swisher  | game |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | comedy | horror | thriller   |

