.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, musician, police-officer, teacher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, june, april
1. the teacher is on the left of the musician##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the teacher##1
5. the musician is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Job           | electrician | teacher    | musician    | police-officer |
| Birthday   | january      | june | february | april       |

