.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, monopoly, mah-jongg
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Game   | snooker | monopoly | whist | mah-jongg   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 